&lt;div&gt;GLC is a leading independent investment banking firm that delivers objective, senior-level advice within a number of industries including: business services, consumer &amp;amp; retail, energy &amp;amp; power, financial services, gaming, general industrials, healthcare, media &amp;amp; telecom, metals &amp;amp; mining and technology.&lt;/div&gt;
