&lt;div&gt;·&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;Current undergraduate or graduate student with an expected graduation date in Summer 2026&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div&gt;·&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;Prior experience in corporate finance, accounting, private equity, investment banking, or related financial services&lt;/div&gt;
