&lt;div&gt;·&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;Proficient in Excel and PowerPoint, as well as preferred experience with other financial information tools such as S&amp;amp;P Capital IQ and PitchBook&lt;/div&gt;

