&lt;p&gt;Analysts will assume significant ownership across all phases of transaction execution, including:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Analyzing companies, industries, capital structures, liquidity profiles, historical financial statements, and projected financial information&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Building financial models and performing valuation analyses&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Conducting industry and company research&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Managing and executing due diligence&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Preparing presentations, board materials, and other client-facing materials&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Leveraging AI-tools to maximize efficiency&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
