&lt;p&gt;GLC Advisors seeks candidates with a demonstrated record of excellence, including:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Exceptional work ethic and intellectual curiosity&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proven self-starter with leadership qualities and analytical aptitude&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Undergraduate degree from an outstanding institution with exceptional academic achievement&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Prior experience working within a bulge-bracket boutique investment bank, or experience in restructuring, leveraged finance, or debt capital markets is preferred, but not required&lt;/li&gt;
